snippet: No longer the best receiver in the N.F.L., or even on his own team, Randy Moss has become a sly veteran, using his wiles to extract yardage.
abstract: San Francisco 49ers wide receiver Randy Moss has, by necessity, become a sly veteran, using his wiles to extract yardage; teammates say Moss has helped wide Michael Crabtree to a breakthrough season.
lead_paragraph: No longer the best receiver in the N.F.L., or even on his own team, Randy Moss has become a sly veteran, using his wiles to extract yardage.

headline.seo: On 49ers, Randy Moss Reinvents Himself as Role Model
